The paper deals with group testing algorithms for resolving broadcast conflicts on a multiple access channel and for identifying dead sensors in a mobile ad hoc wireless network. These problems are related to information theory (cs.IT), distributed systems (cs.DS), network infrastructure (cs.NI), signal processing (cs.SI), and machine learning (cs.LG). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
